Copy mesh as voxel
1) Find furthest verticies of object (at least 90 degree angles)


Voxel creation
1) Create cubes
2) Store cubes
3) Cull cubes to find outer mesh
4) Send outer mesh to be rendered

Destroying Cubes:
1) Find contact point (vertex or fragments)
2) Find lines of contact (velocity and calculated path)
3) Find which cubes are "hit"
4) Mark these cubes as deleted
5) Find any cubes that are not apart of the main mass
6) Mark all cubes that are not connected to this mass.
7) Render all "Alive" cubes
